Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.68,0:26:27.33,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}一直紧跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.56,0:26:32.09,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}当我们乘上光之船
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.27,0:26:37.57,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}那起风时的音符 将会奏响
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.11,0:25:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.96,0:25:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.26,0:25:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion 为什么禁忌的这个名字会…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.66,0:25:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行 搞什么 这个合体
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.33,0:25:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 以前从来没有过这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 Aquarion是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.19,0:25:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 多纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行 只要威瑟石还存在 禁断的男女合体…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.18,0:25:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以往的常识和感觉都四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.04,0:25:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四分五裂地爆裂开
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.89,0:26:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂了 一直珍藏的某种东西 爆发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.40,0:26:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.26,0:26:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这个形态
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.69,0:26:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion 进化了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.17,0:26:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新计数器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.87,0:26:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样久违的 臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以新的姿态出现的禁断名字
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.90,0:26:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.53,0:26:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终焉将如期而至 现在即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.94,0:27:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然说Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.36,0:27:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑浆在颤动
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.60,0:27:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预料之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.32,0:27:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就将你们变成灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.25,0:27:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气味的真正面目是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.19,0:27:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁断的Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.42,0:27:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以Vector Z为头部的合体
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.09,0:27:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion竟然还有别的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.47,0:27:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的不洁 男女合体应该是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.17,0:27:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印被解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.51,0:27:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由那些少年们的手里解开
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.78,0:27:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔君 到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.98,0:27:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是在Aquarion的里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.39,0:27:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evol是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.93,0:27:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evol是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.00,0:27:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.84,0:27:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快从那个男人身边离开
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.73,0:27:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.63,0:27:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢走并驾驶Aquarion的恐怖分子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.36,0:27:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.15,0:27:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔君不是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.52,0:27:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要狡辩了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.59,0:28:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来了 普通人的组合来当头部什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.51,0:28:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教官 司令部传来的强制合体解除要求
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.35,0:28:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就在试了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.89,0:28:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.65,0:28:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.23,0:28:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边的控制一切都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.79,0:28:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然跟那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.31,0:28:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.12,0:28:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长　啊不 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.35,0:28:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.59,0:28:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同于现在的Aquaria样的男女分开的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.69,0:28:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是雌雄同体的胜利之完全体
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.18,0:28:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 神的道具人类怎么能够使用
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.97,0:28:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊这个家伙  虚有其表吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.40,0:28:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出真正的实力上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么 没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.67,0:29:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.91,0:29:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要 没办法的 战斗什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.95,0:29:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不要这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.39,0:29:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被勉强进来的 出去也是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.56,0:29:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 少女 这种状况你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.56,0:29:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔君 逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.74,0:29:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为“我们都是废柴什么的”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.47,0:29:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.03,0:29:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.37,0:29:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方的增援
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.74,0:29:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子不是杂鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.11,0:29:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大型机 同型号的三台
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.75,0:29:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊你们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.53,0:29:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐大人 有回舰命令
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.54,0:29:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我们一起回Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.26,0:29:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云那个老头子的指使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.73,0:30:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Neagula的采取已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.33,0:30:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这之后的战斗是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.18,0:30:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定是否战斗的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.04,0:30:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是等着被干掉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.84,0:30:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好了 我来教你战斗的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.69,0:30:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将拉手上的锁解除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.77,0:30:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.55,0:30:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.26,0:30:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡的Element能力异常地增幅了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.06,0:30:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个小鬼共鸣了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.73,0:30:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是男女机合体
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.28,0:30:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同 和以往的Aquaria完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.63,0:30:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁断的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.81,0:31:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神 神乐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.35,0:31:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这群家伙是来拖后腿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.94,0:31:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.31,0:31:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不需要你来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.64,0:31:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.77,0:31:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.77,0:31:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.81,0:31:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气味 气味
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.55,0:31:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气味的尽头 有黑暗伴随
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.20,0:31:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把别的机体的部分强硬地接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.53,0:31:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样还有那种动作
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.62,0:31:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜过野兽的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.54,0:31:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.09,0:31:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.54,0:31:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的不要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.87,0:31:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊 这个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.48,0:31:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始就一直哭个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.46,0:31:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是战斗中 别分神 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.47,0:32:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 是女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.11,0:32:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 能保护得了她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.03,0:32:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.91,0:32:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.23,0:32:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丧服的结婚仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.27,0:32:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做过的恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.34,0:32:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结 结婚仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.87,0:32:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element能力 绝望之血
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.90,0:32:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的影像刺激到脑部
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.66,0:32:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个场景为什么我们能看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.78,0:32:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.43,0:32:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回禁断之名的Aquarion展示给我们看的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.96,0:32:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预知到的是这样的情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.56,0:32:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝望而最糟的合体
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.24,0:32:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在那里的是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.54,0:32:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.16,0:32:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁边的男人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.00,0:32:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脸给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.34,0:33:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.09,0:33:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.09,0:33:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.97,0:33:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这气味的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.19,0:33:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.75,0:33:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.11,0:33:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.80,0:33:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是你的错 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.14,0:33:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行胡乱的合体 还牵扯进御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.24,0:34:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是你这混蛋的错
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.18,0:34:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.67,0:34:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 心跳加快 兴奋不止
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.42,0:34:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小一直被大家避讳着
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那人置于不顾也是 这力量的错
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.77,0:34:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 决定不再使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.27,0:34:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想要保护御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.10,0:34:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.37,0:34:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却让御子乃经历更加糟糕的境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.47,0:34:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这种人 要保护御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.70,0:34:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.53,0:34:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.55,0:34:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.76,0:34:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.53,0:34:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屏障等级低下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.21,0:35:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去Aquarion会…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.57,0:35:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被神话认可
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.64,0:35:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是自身成为神话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.05,0:35:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔·空 你已拥有这份觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.37,0:35:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 “我们都是废柴什么的”什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.28,0:35:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我这种人混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.10,0:35:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔君很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.05,0:35:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是刚见面
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.09,0:35:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽力地想要保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.68,0:35:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会哭泣呜咽的弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.19,0:35:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.31,0:35:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.01,0:35:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.75,0:35:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.81,0:35:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃的手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.65,0:36:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小巧 纤细的 滑滑的 温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.97,0:36:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.93,0:36:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.06,0:36:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
