Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.08,0:37:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.68,0:38:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.65,0:38:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.68,0:38:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.74,0:38:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.18,0:38:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种瘦弱的男人 把御子乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.55,0:38:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.95,0:38:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着那小鬼和女孩归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.73,0:38:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那男的 能够理解
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.69,0:38:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这女孩 没有一点价值
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.00,0:38:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷登上Aquaria的人不能就这么放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.40,0:39:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.45,0:39:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.54,0:39:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能等待着我 独一无二的人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.22,0:39:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那翱翔在天际的少年的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.82,0:39:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会…
