Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.38,0:39:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Guniss毁坏成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.29,0:40:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有收获吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
